<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/styles/main.css" />
  <title>Listify</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/673aed7dea.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body class="dark bg-gray-950 transition duration-500 ease-in-out">
  <div id="svg_background_dark" class="svg_background pointer-events-none h-screen animate-pulse"></div>
  <div class="animation-rotate grid gap-2">
    <div
      class="animate-pulse flex gap-2 items-center w-64 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
      <i class="fas fa-list text-blue-600"></i>
      <span class="w-full h-1 bg-gray-100"></span>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex gap-2 items-center w-64 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
      <i class="fas fa-list text-blue-600"></i>
      <span class="w-full h-1 bg-gray-100"></span>
    </div>
    <div
      class="animate-pulse flex gap-2 items-center w-64 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
      <i class="fas fa-list text-blue-600"></i>
      <span class="w-full h-1 bg-gray-100"></span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('includes/messages'); %>

  <!-- Begin Main Content -->
  <main class="w-screen h-auto sm:h-screen p-8 grid gap-12">
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto pt-20 sm:pt-24 lg:pt-32">
      <h1
        class="text-slate-900 font-extrabold text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl tracking-tight text-center dark:text-white">
        Organize sua Vida - <span class="text-blue-600">Listify</span></h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto dark:text-slate-400">
        Bem vindo ao <span class="text-blue-600">Listify</span>. Este é um aplicativo de gerenciamento de tarefas para
        que você possa concluir todas as suas tarefas com facilidade.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 sm:mt-10 flex justify-center space-x-6 text-sm">
        <a class="outline-none transition bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded text-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-600/50 focus:shadow-blue-600/50"
          href="/login">Entrar</a>
        <a class="outline-none transition backdrop-blur-sm bg-gray-700/30 hover:bg-blue-700/30 text-white font-bold py-2 px-12 rounded text-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-700/50 focus:shadow-blue-700/50"
          href="/register">Cadastre-se</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-8">

      <div
        class="relative md:flex-1 w-full px-4 py-8 backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/30 dark:bg-slate-600/30 text-white rounded-lg shadow-md border-t-2 border-blue-600 shadow-lg dark:shadow-slate-950">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-blue-700">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-pencil text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-950 dark:text-white">Organize suas tarefas</h2>
        <p class=""></p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base font-semibold text-slate-400">
          <li>Mantenha o <span class="text-blue-600">controle</span> de todas as suas tarefas.</li>
          <li>Marque itens como <span class="text-blue-600">concluídos</span> para melhor visualização.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative md:flex-1 w-full px-4 py-8 backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/30 dark:bg-slate-600/30 text-white rounded-lg shadow-md border-t-2 border-amber-600 shadow-lg dark:shadow-slate-950">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-amber-600">
          <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-950 dark:text-white">Crie suas tarefas</h2>
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-400">Crie e organize <span class="text-amber-600">facilmente</span>
          suas tarefas.</p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative md:flex-1 w-full px-4 py-8 backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/30 dark:bg-slate-600/30 text-white rounded-lg shadow-md border-t-2 border-green-600 shadow-lg dark:shadow-slate-950">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-green-700">
          <i class="fa-regular fa-bell text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-950 dark:text-white">Seja lembrado</h2>
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-400">Com o Listify você pode ter <span
            class="text-green-700">notificações</span> para que você nunca perca um compromisso importante.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button id="theme-toggle"
      class="outline-0 flex justify-center items-center gap-2 w-64 h-12 m-auto transition rounded cursor-pointer backdrop-blur-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-50 bg-gray-300 hover:text-gray-50 hover:bg-gradient-to-r dark:hover:from-blue-500 dark:hover:to-indigo-600 hover:from-yellow-500 hover:to-pink-600 hover:shadow-md dark:hover:shadow-blue-600 hover:shadow-yellow-600">
      <i id="theme-icon" class="fas fa-moon pointer-events-none"></i>
      <span id="theme-text">Dark mode</span>
    </button>
  </main>
  <!-- End Main Content -->
  <script type="module" src="/utils/MessageServer.js"></script>
  <script src="/settings/DarkMode.js"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      darkMode: "class",
    };
  </script>
</body>